  "detailed_description": "Come and help Mad collect the Orbs and get back to his home.<br>MADHACK is a 2D platform game in Retro style, with stages created by hand, with precise controls and that provides fun for all types of players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.poster.avif?t=1669490771\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.webm?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.mp4?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A fun and relaxed adventure for all types of players, who like platform games.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 18 levels for the player to explore and discover all possible paths between each level.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A good challenge for Speedrunners (the game has a native timer).</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.poster.avif?t=1669490771\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.webm?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.mp4?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Come and help Mad collect the Orbs and get back to his home.<br>MADHACK is a 2D platform game in Retro style, with stages created by hand, with precise controls and that provides fun for all types of players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.poster.avif?t=1669490771\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.webm?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/fbafb3e0600accb4ef12ea1ab5e9f316.mp4?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A fun and relaxed adventure for all types of players, who like platform games.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 18 levels for the player to explore and discover all possible paths between each level.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A good challenge for Speedrunners (the game has a native timer).</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.poster.avif?t=1669490771\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.webm?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428790/extras/785bc72fa5c00b88582097815e278282.mp4?t=1669490771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
